{"tid":2491861,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"魔力寶貝正服強勢回歸(47)登入寶貝之你今晚熄唔熄機","createTime":"2021-04-16T15:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T15:52:23.000Z","uid":4516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7eadb4cd2aaf2f6ad09bc7d6da4265613cf303cc","tid":2491861,"uid":4516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:19:13.000Z","msg":"永恒初心最精彩片段！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BScZURkUuMQ&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBScZURkUuMQ%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=c3c40924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=BScZURkUuMQ&amp;feature=youtu.be</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記得拎完獎狀去左邊士兵拎禮包 右邊伏黎<br />\n入雙子 多d hk人<br />\n<br />\nSer已不足一日內玩完（瘋狂斷線）<br />\n電腦game 冇電話版<br />\nMac（所有系統）玩唔到<br />\n<br />\n主程式：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3cvTEox\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3cvTEox&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=7d87e3c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3cvTEox</a><br />\n<br />\n官網：<a href=\"https://cg.originmood.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcg.originmood.com%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=a2e48017\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cg.originmood.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://crossgate-memory.herokuapp.com/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcrossgate-memory.herokuapp.com%2F%23%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=64921bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://crossgate-memory.herokuapp.com/#/</a><br />\n八業巴整既網站<br />\n<br />\n要招小圈子請另開新版<br />\n<br />\n註冊 link <br />\n右上改名遮電話<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3enqJUU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3enqJUU&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=ae80a415\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/3enqJUU</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=211310\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D211310&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=d624b6ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=211310</a><br />\n<br />\n繼承經典內容的《魔力寶貝：永恆初心》2021 年春季上線 採免費制形式推出<br />\n<br />\n熟悉的洗錢內容，支那永恆的騙錢初心，將還給你最經典的斷線《魔力寶貝》，還給你和當年一樣洗錢的感動。不論在哪個世代，bug斷線都會一直陪伴著你。<br />\n<br />\n理想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現實<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下開返ser先算<br />\n<br />\n如果等級不到十級可以去就職領事館找ＮＰＣ可以免費傳送到伊爾村還有聖拉魯卡村（請睇下邊大地圖）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n卡在線的話，在主選單刪除「Assets&gt;data&gt;0-9 folder」即可<br />\n<br />\n解決亂碼<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點樣教大視窗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n將電腦既解像度較低<br />\n<br />\n地圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n揀職可睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=151&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D70151%26snA%3D151%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=e07aece1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=151&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=</a><br />\n<br />\n有用網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://cgsword.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcgsword.com%2F&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4234b965\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cgsword.com/</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/G1.php?bsn=2577\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FG1.php%3Fbsn%3D2577&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=106723e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/G1.php?bsn=2577</a> <br />\n<br />\n亂射速度比較<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=2577&amp;page=&amp;snA=157526&amp;last=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D2577%26page%3D%26snA%3D157526%26last%3D&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4e1b3d9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=2577&amp;page=&amp;snA=157526&amp;last=</a><br />\n<br />\n公式<br />\n<a href=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaNho7VysDGTuizRCQQaptfSWurwtj54nGWS5AN1GBa9o?filename=3yj5uvW.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yj5uvW.png&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=76499079\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaNho7VysDGTuizRCQQaptfSWurwtj54nGWS5AN1GBa9o?filename=3yj5uvW.png</a> <br />\n<br />\n計掉器 <br />\n<a href=\"http://cgsword.com/download.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcgsword.com%2Fdownload.htm&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=5639430c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cgsword.com/download.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n台仔整既QA<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=237&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.gamer.com.tw%2Fforum%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D70151%26snA%3D237%26bpage%3D1%26ltype%3D&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLVUwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=1a8318ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.gamer.com.tw/forum/C.php?bsn=70151&amp;snA=237&amp;bpage=1&amp;ltype=</a>"},{"pid":"2e0f784858437c02e3e8dfa5bd395b52c3a67f00","tid":2491861,"uid":4516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:19:53.000Z","msg":"入到雙16<br />\n求帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650ea58a807f5436867bcfd8bcb7e1f82d8f0a52","tid":2491861,"uid":54721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:20:01.000Z",